						<summary>

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1438, Dhātu (= A.D. 1516-17)</hi> with no further details. It records that king <hi rend="bold">Kṛishṇarāya-Mahārāya</hi> caused the construction of the hundredpillared <hi rend="italic">maṇḍapa</hi> to god <hi rend="bold">Viṭhaladēva</hi> in the year mentioned.</p>						

